Английская версия
gest/telegest
Description
gest/telegest is a small PHP library for interacting with the Telegram Bot API. It is designed to simplify the process of creating and managing Telegram bots by providing a convenient interface for working with the Telegram API.

Features
Sending messages and media files
Handling incoming messages and commands
Support for asynchronous HTTP requests using Guzzle and ReactPHP
Dependency injection using PHP-DI
Installation
You can install the library using Composer:

bash
Копировать код
composer require gest/telegest
Usage Example
php
Копировать код
require 'vendor/autoload.php';

use Gest\Telegest\Bot;

$bot = new Bot('YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_API_TOKEN');

$bot->onMessage(function($message) use ($bot) {
    $chatId = $message->chat->id;
    $bot->sendMessage($chatId, 'Hello, world!');
});

$bot->run();
Requirements
PHP 7.4 or higher
Guzzle HTTP 7.8 or higher
ReactPHP (Event Loop, HTTP, Promise)
PHP-DI 7.0 or higher
